Author: pazzesco
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO][ICO] CarVDB – A Decentralized Platform for the Automotive World
Body: Any unsold tokens after Soft Cap is reached will be distributed among the rest of the investors proportionally to their contribution.  A very simplistic example, let's say there are only two investors, one has invested 1 ETH the other has invested 9 ETH. We have 1000 CAR tokens remaining. The first investor will get 10%, i.e. 100 CAR tokens, the second one will get 90%, i.e. 900 CAR tokens.  The real distribution will be the same but in a larger scale. Hopefully we will never get to that!

Author: pazzesco
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO][ICO] CarVDB – A Decentralized Platform for the Automotive World
Body: The remaining tokens will not be burned. They will be distributed between all the contributers.  Price paid by the investors should not be impacted. Distributing the remaining tokens to the people who already have invested would mean that they would get more tokens for the same price.

Author: pazzesco
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO][ICO] CarVDB – A Decentralized Platform for the Automotive World
Body: Our platform will have multiple applications - before buying a vehicle you can check its full history, you can safely pay it with CAR tokens, you can make a deposit, purchase insurance and spare parts, arrange maintenance and more. For common people it will be a lot easier and safer to buy/sell a vehicle and manage all the tasks related to the ownership.  As to competitors, there are none in the blockchain industry. Mainstream, our competitors will be the biggest auto classifieds websites and all platform that provide online insurance. No other platform provide services for arranging vehicle maintenance or payment for such maintenance with digital currency.  So we have competiotrs in some areas but aboslutely no competitors in others.  You can find out more at our website www.carvdb.com

Author: pazzesco
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO][ICO] CarVDB – A Decentralized Platform for the Automotive World
Body: A lot of people have been asking for insight on the CarVDB Black Card Benefits they receive when investing with our ICO so here they go:        · Yearly bonus of 500 CAR Tokens to be spent by the card holders as per their desire.       · CarVDB user profile marked as “Founding Member”, which entitles each card holder to priority customer service and lifetime no transaction fees on the CarVDB platform.       · Up to 25% discount on insurance premiums       · Up to 60% discount on purchases of vehicle spare parts and accessories       · Priority maintenance appointment at any of our Service Center partners. This means no more waiting for 2 weeks to get your vehicle inspected / repaired. You get your appointment within the next two business days.       · Up to 30% discount on vehicle maintenance / repair jobs       · Car Rental Benefits — card holders get complimentary vehicle upgrade and premium prices at some of the major rental companies.       · Additional one time exclusive offers, services and discounts provided by CarVDB or our partners.  THINGS TO REMEMBER:       · There will be only 500 cards issued, ever.       · Cars with numbers 001–250 will be issued to the CarVDB ICO contributors who have made the 250 largest ETH contributions. (Maximum individual contribution is 1,500 ETH).       · Cars with numbers 251 –500 will be issued to the CarVDB ICO contributors who have made the first 250 ETH contributions irrespective of the contribution amount.      If you wish to invest with us please register here and follow the provided instructions.  Thank you for helping us build the next generation automotive platform!

Author: pazzesco
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO][ICO] CarVDB – A Decentralized Platform for the Automotive World
Body: This is a very good question, thank you!  The platform was initially designed as an alternative to the over complicated and overburdened auto classifieds websites.  During the first couple of years, the platform has been constantly under improvement to reach the design and functionality that you can currently see.  With the rise of the blockchain technology we realized there is much more that we can offer and really expand the platform to deliver a truly end-to-end solution to all vehicle owners.  The roadmap that you see on our website is our plan for the next 5 years.

Author: pazzesco
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO][ICO] CarVDB – A Decentralized Platform for the Automotive World
Body: All projects related to crypto currencies are by definition long term. Have you seen any blockchain project (except Bitcoin and Ethereum) that has wide spread real world user base? Nobody has. This is something that needs time to grow.  However, there are two major differences between CarVDB and the majority of the other blockchain projects:  First, we already have a working platform in place, which is available to everyone and can be used as we speak. Second, the technology that we are going to integrate into our platform does not rely solely on blockchain functionality, hence people can start to use it as soon as the development is complete.  In the long term, the main "currency" on our platform will be the CAR token. We however plan to also use FIAT money until the users get used to the token  and for convenience of those groups of people who prefer more traditional ways of payment.  As to payments with other coins like Bitcoin or Ethereum, we have not ruled out their integration and we might do it if it makes sense. In order for this to happen, people should start to use them as payment method first rather than holding as means of investment. If there is wide spread usage and there is a demand, we will surely integrate other coins.

Author: pazzesco
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO][ICO] CarVDB – A Decentralized Platform for the Automotive World
Body: CarVDB.com  CarVDB: The First Decentralized End-to-End Platform for the Automotive World     Pre-ICO starts at 9:30am UTC on 13th March 2018   Website | Whitepaper | Twitter | Facebook | Telegram | BOUNTY Thread | Github   Crowdsale Progress:     What is CarVDB?  CarVDB is blockchain based decentralized platform aiming to revolutionize the automotive world. The Platform in designed around four core modules:  ..................................................... Free to use & transparent Available to private and professional sellers Sell any type of vehicle Buy any type of vehicle Rent any type of vehicle Both private and dealership offers available Vehicle offers with fixed price or with bidding option Send and Receive deposit for a vehicle Safely pay for a vehicle in CAR Tokens Check full vehicle history (maintenance, accidents, mileage, etc.) Offer and receive warranty for a vehicle Possibility to make a secure purchase via Smart Contract or offline Special Features available for professional sellers and Dealerships ..................................................... Free to use & transparent Available to private and professional sellers Automatic insurance calculator Offer or purchase vehicle insurance Personalized insurance quotes based on historical data Insurance expiration reminders Control panel to manage policies, assess risk and control cost Targeting feature for customers that might need insurance Fully automated processes - from quote to claim Physical signature available Easy data exchange with other insurance systems Accept payments in CAR Tokens as well as FIAT currencies Possibility to make a secure purchase via Smart Contract or offline ..................................................... Free to use & transparent Available to private and professional sellers Timed and Live webcast bidding Organize one or more auctions at a time for multiple items Real time, high quality video and audio Possibility to place autobids Possibility to use Buy Now (Fixed Price) feature Auction sniping Auto relisting Real time updates to all bidders Automatic handling of ending auctions Accept payments in CAR Tokens as well as FIAT currencies All auction bids & purchases are secured via Smart Contracts ..................................................... Free to use & transparent Available to both vehicle owners and Service Centers Full vehicle history available - maintenance, accidents, mileage Reminders for upcoming maintenance to owners & Service Centers Owners can manually schedule a vehicle maintenance Rpair manuals and step by step instructions available Easy management of quotes & invoices from booking to completion Targeting feature for customers that need maintenance services Analytics features to analyze job duration and resource utilization Workforce optimization and resource planning Automated invoicing process Automated bookkeeping – track revenue, expenses & profits Supply Management features - view historical order quantities, track purchases & inventory, create orders, pay invoices Track and manage jobs related to insurance events Accept payments in CAR Tokens as well as FIAT currencies All maintenance jobs are secured via Smart Contracts Where is CarVDB available? The CarVDB Platform is currently available in United States and Spain via two separate portals:   Where is CarVDB available?  The CarVDB Platform is currently available in United States and Spain via two separate portals:   ............................................................................... ............................................................................... CarVDB.com MiCocheNuevo.es   We are targeting for worldwide implementation according to the below map:     Crowdsale  The ICO will be held in seven waves as per the below table:       Use of Funds  ............................................................................... 46% – Product Development - almost half of the ICO funds will be directly invested in further product development in order to meet the platform design specifications and functionality. 20% – Marketing and User Acquisition - the amount dedicated for marketing purposes is set at one-fifth of total funds since we estimate amount required in order to achieve steady and increasing user base which in turn will allow for further platform growth. 16% – Operational Capital - a portion of the funds gathered will be used to cover for operational expenses related to platform services like insurance quotes, guaranteed deposits, vehicle warranty, etc. 10% – Reserve Capital - One-tenth of the raised funds will be held as reserve in case of unexpected events during the first two years of the post ICO project. 8% – ICO related cost - Approximately 8% of the total amount gathered during the ICO (pre-ICO) will be used to cover for all the expenses for the ICO event.     CAR Token Distribution  ............................................................................... 50% (49,978,560) will be distributed during the ICO. 36% (36,000,000) tokens will be reserved for the CarVDB pool. The tokens in this pool will be distributed during a period of one year to the first CarVDB users for free according to their contribution in terms of content and quality. 14% (14,000,000) tokens will be reserved for the founding members, development team, early hires and advisors. 1% (21,440) special tokens will reserved for the top contributing users/members (or users who add value) to the platform.   Roadmap     Team & Advisory Board     !!!IMPORTANT - BOUNTIES WILL SOO BE ANOUNCES SO KEEP AN EYE ON THE THREAD
